comment: [Incidental or immaterial] Pierce (LAC) and Pachulia (DAL) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Griffin (LAC) establishes a position next to Matthews (DAL), and gives him the room to avoid the contact.
Pachulia (DAL) makes incidental contact with Griffin (LAC) that does not cause him to lose control of his dribble.
Pachulia (DAL) and Pierce (LAC) briefly engage under the basket.
Nowitzki (DAL) impedes Paul (LAC) as he tries to go around him, affecting his RSBQ on the perimeter.
RATR shows that Jordan (LAC) makes contact with Williams' (DAL) arm, affecting his shot attempt.
Matthews (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Paul's (LAC) drive to the basket.
Griffin (LAC) dislodges Pachulia (DAL) and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Pierce (LAC) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot when he gathers the pass, then moves it to create space.
Anderson (DAL) cleanly blocks Stephenson's (LAC) layup attempt.
Crawford (LAC) commits a take foul on Felton (DAL).
